snippet: Ranked eighth in the world at the start of the year, Brandt Snedeker already is halfway to his goal of reaching No. 1 with his two-stroke victory at the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am.
abstract: Brandt Snedeker wins Pebble Beach National Pro-Am golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Ranked eighth in the world at the start of the year, Brandt Snedeker already is halfway to his goal of reaching No. 1 with his two-stroke victory at the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am.

headline.seo: Snedeker Wins Pebble Beach Pro-Am in a Stretch That Amazes Even Him
